                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 825.001.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Pierrepont</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-09-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 6, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Pierrepont states that after a short illness the Vice President of the
                    Republic of Chile, Señor Fernandez Albano, died this day.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
